               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus "Miracles of Jesus": 7 miracles (fols. 1r-16v)
 -
                     A short (<term key="Qene" ana="#Qene"/>qǝne?) poem about the second coming of Jesus (አመ፡ ትመጽእ፡ ለኰንኖ፡ ምስለ፡ ደመ፡
                     ገቦ፡ ወአዕጋር...).</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="16v"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus "Miracles of Jesus": 7 miracles</title>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
